<section class="text-gray-600 body-font">
  <div class="container mx-auto flex px-5 py-24 md:flex-row flex-col justify-center items-center">
    <div class="lg:max-w-lg lg:w-full md:w-2/5 w-5/6 mb-10 md:mb-0">
      <%= image_tag('logo.jpg', class: "object-cover object-center w-full h-full") %>
    </div>
    <div class="lg:flex-grow md:w-3/5 lg:pl-24 md:pl-16 flex flex-col md:items-start md:text-left items-center text-center">
      <h1 class="title-font sm:text-4xl text-3xl mb-4 font-medium text-gray-900">YumMeetで
        <br class="hidden lg:inline-block">小さなお子様連れでも安心
        <br class="hidden lg:inline-block">家族みんなで楽しめる
        <br class="hidden lg:inline-block">飲食店の情報を手に入れよう！
      </h1>
      <div class="flex justify-center">
        <%= link_to(login_path, class: "inline-flex text-gray-700 bg-gray-100 border-0 py-2 px-6 focus:outline-none hover:bg-gray-200 rounded text-lg") do %>
        早速ログイン
        <% end %>
        <button class="ml-4 inline-flex text-white bg-indigo-500 border-0 py-2 px-6 focus:outline-none hover:bg-indigo-600 rounded text-lg">
        投稿を見る</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="container px-5 py-24 mx-auto">
    <div class="flex items-center lg:w-3/5 mx-auto border-b pb-10 mb-10 border-gray-200 sm:flex-row flex-col">
      <div class="sm:w-32 sm:h-32 h-20 w-20 sm:mr-10 inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-indigo-100 text-indigo-500 flex-shrink-0">
        <%= image_tag('top_mother.png', class: "object-cover object-center w-full h-full") %>
      </div>
      <div class="flex-grow sm:text-left text-center mt-6 sm:mt-0">
        <h2 class="text-gray-900 text-lg title-font font-medium mb-2">小さな子供を連れての食事の悩みって沢山ある！</h2>
        <li class="leading-relaxed text-base">子供が食べれるメニューがあるか</li>
        <li class="leading-relaxed text-base">本当に子連れOKな雰囲気のお店なのか</li>
        <li class="leading-relaxed text-base">ベビーカーや離乳食の持ち込みはOKなのか　等</li>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="flex items-center lg:w-3/5 mx-auto border-b pb-10 mb-10 border-gray-200 sm:flex-row flex-col">
      <div class="flex-grow sm:text-left text-center mt-6 sm:mt-0">
        <h2 class="text-gray-900 text-lg title-font font-medium mb-2">本当に気になることって沢山あるけれど・・・</h2>
        <li class="leading-relaxed text-base">たまには息抜きしたい</li>
        <li class="leading-relaxed text-base">おしゃれな食事で日頃の疲れを癒したい</li>
        <li class="leading-relaxed text-base">何より誰かに作ってもらう食事は美味しい！</li>
      </div>
      <div class="sm:w-32 sm:order-none order-first sm:h-32 h-20 w-20 sm:ml-10 inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-indigo-100 text-indigo-500 flex-shrink-0">
        <%= image_tag('top_food.png', class: "object-cover object-center w-full h-full") %>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="flex items-center lg:w-3/5 mx-auto pb-10 mb-10 border-gray-200 sm:flex-row flex-col">
      <div class="sm:w-32 sm:h-32 h-20 w-20 sm:mr-10 inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-indigo-100 text-indigo-500 flex-shrink-0">
        <%= image_tag('top_share.png', class: "object-cover object-center w-full h-full") %>
      </div>
      <div class="flex-grow sm:text-left text-center mt-6 sm:mt-0">
        <h2 class="text-gray-900 text-lg title-font font-medium mb-2">YumMeetではリアルな声が聴ける！！</h2>
        <li class="leading-relaxed text-base">実際に子連れで行った人のレビューが見れる</li>
        <li class="leading-relaxed text-base">店舗に関する情報交換ができる</li>
        <li class="leading-relaxed text-base">色んなお店に行く楽しみができる</li>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="flex justify-center">
      <%= link_to(login_path, class: "inline-flex text-white bg-indigo-500 border-0 py-2 px-6 focus:outline-none hover:bg-indigo-600 rounded text-lg") do %>
        早速ログイン
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
